it pertains to the question I
asked.

896
01:28:46,125 --> 01:28:49,707
Or our meeting. Or
a career in your desired field.

897
01:28:49,708 --> 01:28:52,040
Oh no, it's related.

898
01:28:52,041 --> 01:28:55,583
Well, you might think so, but
I'm not seeing it.

899
01:28:57,583 --> 01:28:59,500
Trust me, it's all related.



